<activity xml:id="act-dosManerasDeSumar" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Andre started with the hundreds, but Clare started with the ones. They both used place value, but went in different order. They both added hundreds and hundreds, tens and tens, and ones and ones. They both had to add up the hundreds, tens, and ones at the end.</p>
  </solution>


